Package com.hannonhill.cascade.api.asset.home

Interface FolderContainedAsset

All Superinterfaces:
BaseAsset, NamedAsset, PermissionsCapableAsset
All Known Subinterfaces:
Block, FeedBlock, File, Folder, Format, IndexBlock, MetadataAwareAsset, Page, PublishableAsset, Reference, ScriptFormat, Symlink, Template, TextBlock, TwitterFeedBlock, XHTMLDataDefinitionBlock, XMLBlock, XSLTFormat
public interface FolderContainedAsset extends PermissionsCapableAsset
Describes the common properties that any asset contained within a folder shares.
Since:
4.7

      void setParentFolderIdentifier(Identifier parentFolderIdentifier)
      Set the parent folder's identifier, which specifies the relationship between this asset and its containing folder.

      Changing this will have the effect of moving an asset.

      Parameters:
      parentFolderIdentifier - the identifier identifying the new parent folder
